snippet.title: Rocket League - Official 4K Cinematic Free To Play Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to TAKE YOUR SHOT, because Rocket League Free to Play begins on September 23. Read more details at rocketleague.com/news/rocket-league-free-to-play-arrives-september-23/

Speed into the high-octane hybrid of arcade-style soccer and vehicular mayhem featuring cross-platform play and progression, Challenges, Tournaments, and more! Download and play Rocket League for free on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and now Epic Games Store! 

#TakeYourShot #RocketLeageFreeToPlay #DownloadRocketLeague #FreeRocketLeague
